 Work with Purpose 



AngloGold Ashanti is aware that we operate in a complex environment that also affects the communities and countries in which we operate. This complexity can provide you with an opportunity to enjoy and benefit from work in a variety of different roles and on a variety of different projects. Our work culture embraces diversity, nurtures innovation, rewards performance and develops people. Our capability to grow depends on our people, thus we are consistently looking to recruit, engage and retain people for the AngloGold Ashanti of the future. 
 
